iOS v1.8 Release note TalkBox v1.8 Style Up your TalkBox Introduce Themes and Friend Suggestions. You can change the look and feel of TalkBox and even make your own theme and publish to Theme Store via our StyleUp portal. Learn more about on http: styleup.talkboxapp.com Spotlight Feature: Theme Store with 2 new themes built in Simplicity Snowy Friend suggestions Add: Group conversation now support custom naming a Share button under your profile to share your username directly Add Recent sent emoticons New Invite tab Fix: Optimize performance in Recent Tab and Conversation screen Optimize app start up speed Fix texting display and input Fix some devices having difficulties during startup Minor bug fixes

New Functions: 1. Now supports English Chinese Traditional Chinese Simplified . TalkBox s interface language can be set by iPhone system language setting. 2. Added fast switch navigation in Conversation page. In each conversation page once a new message arrives you can swipe on the screen from right to left to switch to the latest conversation. If there is no any new message you can also switch a conversation between the current one and previous one by swiping horizontally on screen. Improvement: 1. fixed incorrect voice message receiving timestamp. 2. fixed the crash after rejecting friend request. 3. fixed friend list synchronization from Facebook Connect. 4. fixed the problem that a single voice message would play several times. 5. fixed Twitter login problem. 6. fixed some other minor bugs.

New Features: 1 Fully supported on all iPod Touch. You can now use the built in microphone on iPod Touch 4 2 Save 10 15 of battery when comparing to v1.0 and running faster at the same time 3 Add Friends directly from a group chat session just tap the group member button in conversation view and you will notice a sign next to those people not in your contact list 4 You can now send photos hint: try sending photos but be careful with what you send to different agents and see what will happen 5 Agent Twitter : you can add Agent Twitter. She is a helpful agent to post your voice to your twitter. You can add Agent Twitter by adding username Twitter 6 Message resending and re fetching: Never miss a single message again 7 Enhance accessibility for vision impaired people 8 Usage statistics added Check network data consumed and message counts in the Settings tab 9 Remove all saved messages an option added inside the Usage section 10 Swipe to delete will remove voice clips permanently from the device 11 Allow password customization In addition there are over 80 modification and bug fixes. Below are the major ones: Fixed sometimes no bubbles shown in conversation view when recording Fixed iOS 4.2 freezes when waking up from background mode Fixed bug with proximity detection i.e. switching sound output from speaker to earpiece Fixed the bubble will be expanding for too long when receiving new messages Fixed the stop button won t flip back in recent conversation view Fixed the sound crashing problem. Fixed stop button won t flip in Recent Conversation Fixed unread count incorrectly shown in recent conversation. Fixed when holding talk button sometimes the beep sound will start coming after the recording instead right before it Fixed avatar mismatched in Contact List Added Terms of Services in Settings Added SMS invitation Added Forget Password in Login Screen Allow change password in My Profile Remove unnecessary permissions granted from Facebook Connect
